Campus.
Istanbul Şehir University has three campuses West Campus, East Campus and South Campus all of them are located in Altunizade,Istanbul. and also in the same time Istanbul Şehir University is developing its main campus in Dragos, Istanbul, which will enter in service in 2014. Currently, lectures are held at the Altunizade Campus.
